            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-8b3851c016c3387a-f3bcb9 twpub-8b3851c016c3387a-245572 twpub-8b3851c016c3387a-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\">This book is dedicated to my good friend &amp; comrade<br>\nMy Wife<br>\nL.F.B.</p></div>"
